<div class="container">
<div id="faq">
<div class="row">
<h1>How does Mandarin Minds work?</h1>

<div class="icon">
	        	<%= image_tag "faq.png", class:"action" %>
</div>

<p>Here is our FAQ list of the most common questions we get about Mandarin Minds. If you still have questions, you can always chat with us to learn more!</p>

<p>See <a href="/what-we-offer">What We Offer</a> for an introduction to our services.</p>
</div>
<div class="question"><p><i class="fa fa-plus"> </i><i class="fa fa-minus"> </i><b>What is a free trial lesson?</b></p></div>

<p class="answer">A free trial lesson allows you to try out half a lesson (25 minutes) to get a feel for what a lesson is and what to expect. From here you will be able to determine if you are comfortable with this style of learning. During this lesson you will discuss your goals and appropriate course material will be recommended by the teacher.</p>

<div class="question"><p><i class="fa fa-plus"> </i><i class="fa fa-minus"> </i><b>When can I take lessons?</b></p></div>

<p class="answer">We have classes available from Monday to Saturday. For further details log in to see each teachers' individual timetable.</p>

<div class="question"><p><i class="fa fa-plus"> </i><i class="fa fa-minus"> </i><b>I would like to learn Mandarin, how can you help me?</b></p></div>

<p class="answer">Whether you are a professional, an organisation or simply learning the language out of interest we have a suitable package available for you. To be able to understand your requirements we ask you to sign up for a free trial lesson and discuss your goals with our teachers.</p>

<div class="question"><p><i class="fa fa-plus"> </i><i class="fa fa-minus"> </i><b>Can I have a class with any teacher?</b></p></div>

<p class="answer">After signing up you will be able to view a brief bio of the teachers by clicking the â€˜Teacher' tab on the  sidebar. Once you have chosen the most suitable teacher for your needs you can book a lesson at your leisure. Please note, it is not possible to book a class less than 48hrs before the scheduled lesson time.</p>

<div class="question"><p><i class="fa fa-plus"> </i><i class="fa fa-minus"> </i><b>Can I work with the same tutor each time?</b></p></div>

<p class="answer">Absolutely, when you book a class you can filter our calendar system to only show the teacher of your choice. However you are free to book with any teacher you wish and are not locked in to having the same one every time.</p>

<div class="question"><p><i class="fa fa-plus"> </i><i class="fa fa-minus"> </i><b>How do the video lessons work? Do I need any special software?</b></p></div>

<p class="answer">Our teachers utilise the free video-calling software <a href="http://www.skype.com">Skype</a> to contact you and so'll you need to have a Skype account and downloaded the program before you can partake in any lessons. Once you've signed up we only need your username so that our teachers can get in touch with you. If you prefer you can instead use the Skype app, available on most smart phone app stores.</p>

<div class="question"><p><i class="fa fa-plus"> </i><i class="fa fa-minus"> </i><b>How do I communicate with my teachers?</b></p></div>

<p class="answer">At the conclusion of your first lesson with a new teacher she will provide you with her e-mail address which you can use to exchange materials. Teachers will be unable to arrange lessons via e-mail, so please book lessons yourself within the portal.</p>

<div class="question"><p><i class="fa fa-plus"> </i><i class="fa fa-minus"> </i><b>What time is the online calendar linked to?</b></p></div> 

<p class="answer">Our calendar is linked to China (GMT +8).</p>

<div class="question"><p><i class="fa fa-plus"> </i><i class="fa fa-minus"> </i><b>Can I cancel a lesson?</b></p></div>

<p class="answer">You are able to cancel an uncoming booked lesson at any time. If you cancel your class more than 24 hours in advance you will not be charged for the lesson. Classes cancelled within 24 hours of the scheduled start time will incur the full class fee though.</p>

<div class="question"><p><i class="fa fa-plus"> </i><i class="fa fa-minus"> </i><b>Can I get a refund on my package?</b></p></div>

<p class="answer">Only in special circumstances will we offer refunds on packages and this must be discussed with the administrative department.</p>

<div class="question"><p><i class="fa fa-plus"> </i><i class="fa fa-minus"> </i><b>Can I review my previous lessons?</b></p></div>

<p class="answer">Most definitely! At the end of each class the teacher will provide feedback on areas in which you need to focus. Homework will be assigned to those who ask for it and this will guide the students on how to review the previous materials.</p>

<div class="question"><p><i class="fa fa-plus"> </i><i class="fa fa-minus"> </i><b>I have more questions, who can help me?</b></p></div>

<p class="answer">If you have more questions please send an email to sales@mandarinminds.com and we will get back to you as soon as we can.</p>
</div>

<style type="text/css">
	.fa-plus, .fa-minus {
		display: none;
	}
</style>

